Vagrant-

Features of Vagrant- 
1. Network
2. Sync Folders
3. Vagrant BOxfile
4. Provider Customizations
5. Provisioners
6. Multi-Machine Vagrant
Q: Where you should write the vagrantfile?
If we are working on a java project, the project directory structure looks like-
project
-src
--main
---java
---resources
---webapp
-----web-INF
-----web.xml
-POM.xml
-Vagrant configration file
